BMBuildKit

A new era for FPGA programming

Quick-start is just 5min away! ⏱️

Built on dagger.io

Docker-like simple!

Designed for emulating the experience of a container build via Docker. You define a BMFile and an FPGA board, the rest is on us.

Program FPGA on the cloud... if you want to

Get your firmware from any container registry and program your FPGA with a single command. And yes, CI/CD is never been easier.

Prototype as you want!

Your firmwares will be tagged like a usual container image, thus keeping track of all your experiments. Comparing the performances will be a walk in the park.
